CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

March 24, 2008

[Cite as 03/24/2008 Case Announcements, 2008-0hio-1310.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2007-1741. State v. Lang.

Stark C.P. No. 2006CR1824A. This cause is pending before the court as a death penalty appeal from the Court of Common Pleas of Stark County. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion to unseal portions of the record filed under seal,

It is ordered by the court that the motion is granted as to the jury questionnaires and excuse list, and denied as to the grand jury materials.
